# ROADMAP

## Objective

A chrome extension that streamline my, if not others', HN experience.

## Functions

Wider ReadItLater support
Easier to share to social media
SVM then ConvolutionNet recommendation system
Comment at the bottom of the page

## Plan
Use eventpage to handle learning process
Store data using Dropbox API; store preference using chrome sync
Integration of API
Recommendation system
ReadItLater

